<h3>emacs spell checking tips</h3>

<p>Call <code class='elisp-ƒ'>flyspell-mode</code> to turn on spell checker as you type.
Call again to turn off.</p>

<p>Call
<code class='elisp-ƒ'>flyspell-buffer</code>
to spell check whole buffer.</p>

<p>Call
<code class='elisp-ƒ'>flyspell-goto-next-error</code>
【<kbd>Ctrl</kbd>+<kbd>,</kbd>】
to move cursor to next error.
(only when <code class='elisp-ƒ'>flyspell-mode</code> is on.)
</p>

<p>Call
<code class='elisp-ƒ'>flyspell-auto-correct-word</code>
【<kbd>Ctrl</kbd>+<kbd>.</kbd>】
to correct the word under cursor.
Press the key again to swap to next suggestion.</p>

<p>Call
<code class='elisp-ƒ'>ispell-word</code>
【<kbd>Alt</kbd>+<kbd>$</kbd>】
to check spelling of current word.</p>
</div>
 